Gard National Nature Park (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 10" captionStartId="F10" captionText="Figure 10. Representative habitats for the herpetofauna in the Mykolaiv Oblast: A. habitat of Coronella austriaca near the village of Zaichevsk; B. habitat of Zamenis longissimus near the village of Grushivka; C. habitat of Podarcis tauricus near the village of Trykhaty; D. Buzk's Gard National Nature Park. Photographs by V. Strenada (A), O. Oskyrko (B, C, D)." figureDoi="10.3897/herpetozoa.34.e62459.figure10" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536310" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">10D</figureCitation>
